Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,======================================== TEXT ========================================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.62,0:00:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,大小姐　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,请问是这本吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,您是要用来做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,关于这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.61,0:02:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,小云雀　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,成绩如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也就普普通通
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那么从明天起放暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.42,0:02:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在夏令营前请务必保重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,夏令营前…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,以上　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,第一学期结课
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:22.62,Title,,0,0,0,,{@\an8\fs60\fn方正综艺_GBK\c&HF1B368&\pos(644,446)}我们的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,转啊转
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,等等牡丹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那样乱转的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小牡丹！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,乌…乌贼先生满天转…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,总之…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,去那里休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,垃圾如我　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,竟不知天高地厚的亢奋起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,明天起就是暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:03:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,想着可以和大家各种玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不知不觉就…轱辘轱辘转起圈来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,太羞人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,大家高兴了都会转起圈的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.51,0:03:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,转啊转
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好像也不那么常见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是小莲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,小莲是你叫的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小响也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说不要随意叫小响…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,天气微热　小憩一番
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,小憩？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不介意的话　要去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 卡拉OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,卡拉OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哼 昨天满脸通红的女店员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然厚脸皮的把这个送给了莲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,想去我想去卡拉OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,机会难得　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那就恭敬不如从命了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,难不成！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是担心听了我难听歌声　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,耳朵会烂掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙心眼好坏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,都说我没那么想！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,从未去过卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就由我这个卡拉OK大师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,响亲自来指导你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好呀 走啦走啦小云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一二一二一二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\fn方正综艺_GBK\bord2\shad0\frz352.8\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H8D7FE1&\move(412,202,788,202,23,5945)\fax0.15\fay0.01}卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,响唱的真的好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是的　
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这旋律十分熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,牡丹经常来卡拉OK吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.25,0:05:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的　
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是第一次进卡拉OK包厢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,因为家里有唱K设施　
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔会去用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,设施…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是的　
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,除此之外还有各种设施
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,请各位一定抽空来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那就明天吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那明天去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好的　
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,非常欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,也好啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,喂你们根本没听响唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,来 下一首是你　
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:05:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,云雀丘瑠璃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这　这就轮到我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,见…见笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,云雀唱的超好听！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,什么嘛　
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是会唱么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,云雀同学的嗓音十分动听
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不太清楚近来的流行歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这是很久之前听的一首…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,CD吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不　
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是母亲边打理庭园边哼唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚查了一下歌词才知道曲名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此　
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好棒　云雀同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来轮到我唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,花子同学　请加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么　
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,耳朵要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,牡丹撑住！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这是麦的蜂鸣声吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,可她还没唱　
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,离扩音器也很远
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,每次去卡拉OK　
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我拿起话筒时一定会发出刺耳声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.75,0:07:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,各位好呀　齐聚一堂真热闹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,猫尾草！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,暂时要见不到大家了　来道个别
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,道别？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,暑假期间我要去检查身体异常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就像住院体检一样对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,猫了个尾草
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那么作为饯别礼 献唱一曲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,猫尾草 猫尾草 猫尾草
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8}猫猫猫猫尾草高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,猫猫猫猫尾…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,猫猫猫猫尾 加时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不加好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,「猫猫猫尾猫尾」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,猫尾草就这样表演了精彩的Rap
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,卡拉OK大会就这样结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.51,0:08:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,蝉先生还在叫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天卡拉OK结束之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,猫尾草的Rap就一直在脑海里打转
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,猫猫猫尾猫尾的那首歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,又会想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那就用其他能停留在耳朵里的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,来忘记猫尾草的歌怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,比如说？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,CM里的「好吃好吃」之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这次那个反而会被记住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:09:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那就「红霉青霉黑霉全都解决掉」CM的歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你还来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但是果然还是猫猫猫尾猫尾对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉看到我的脸后有些害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我的表情真的那么可怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 是平常的小云雀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 那又是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这全都是猫尾草的Rap的错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是大海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,小云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,快看快看 螃蟹 是螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我咬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,花子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,海鸥海鸥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,话说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真是吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这些竟然全部都是人造的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是妹妹为了不能去海水浴的我拜托别人做的设施
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.37,0:10:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,实在是太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,能邀请大家真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,牡丹 你有妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,和耗钱费事如路边石子一般的我不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,妹妹运动万能而且很开朗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,钓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,里面也和真的大海一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,比赛谁先到那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,意识恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,响到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你在潜水的时候失去意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,莲同学的应急措施真是太科学了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,应急措施
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,喂不要睡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是安打
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:11:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,赛点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,然后大家和醒过来的莲同学一起玩了切西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,写下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来是镇上的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\an7\fs60\fn方正康体_GBK\bord6\shad0\3c&HC6E0F7&\pos(342.667,188.667)}大型烟花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\an7\fs60\fn方正康体_GBK\c&H4BD8FB&\bord2\shad0\3c&H5585DD&\pos(342.667,188.667)}大型烟花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,花子 这不是正好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,今天只掉到了河里一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,果然掉河了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那走散的话就在这里集合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那就赶快去逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候买的乌贼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\fr270\bord4\fn@DFKanTeiRyu-W11\pos(252,108)\3c&H1953D7&}苹果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\fr270\fn@DFKanTeiRyu-W11\c&H144ADF&\pos(252,108)\3c&H76CCF7&}苹果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\fs28\b1\c&H0C0AE9&\3c&H4AC0F9&\bord3\frz8.638\fax-0.15\pos(774,162)}棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\an1\bord3\fax-0.46\fn@方正大黑_GBK\fs23\c&H0539B4&\3c&H0638C3&\frz-90\pos(726.666,173.333)}巧克力香蕉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\an1\fax-0.46\fn@方正大黑_GBK\fs23\c&H0539B4&\3c&H0BC6F2&\frz-90\pos(726.666,173.333)}巧克力香蕉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,盯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,散开 散开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\c&H0D1DA6&\3c&H7FCBFD&\bord2\fn@方正粗圆_GBK\fr270\fs30\pos(628,120)}章鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,小云雀她们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说我们走散了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那就去集合的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来去吃那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,已经吃够多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,起码想成功一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,响和花小泉同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,她们人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,响明明都听她们的在这里等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,猫尾草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,会走散的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,都叫你等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,猫尾草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不要管那家伙不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,快点回去正门…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8}小响 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 听人说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,别…别留下我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上的学校原来是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次进来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才好像传来了响的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,从哪来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会出现什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,小响 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么呢  以为我会害怕就大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,咦  小响很害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说响怎么会害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那去看看那边的教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是恶灵干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,点不亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,很好这样就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好多大叔的人像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\bord0\xshad5\yshad-3\an8\fn楷体\b1\c&HE3CFCC&\4c&H503A2F&\pos(640,86.667)}初代校长 堀川照三
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是校长的像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,有那么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好像都在笑好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,响也不知道哪里可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你看再和你打招呼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8}快从这里出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,学园祭的小道具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这个颧骨到下颚骨的肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,说明了他幸福的成长了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,够了 回大门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,花子她们一定也在那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在唱歌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那种令人怀念的 触动人心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有点害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.63,0:18:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,第七代校长是女性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,了解历代校长有什么用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,快点回到原来的正门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都没听到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不听到了 肯定听到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是校长们在说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你不要说这种话了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这个歌声 有点可怕还感觉心里痒痒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,说到盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有个传说是说一套渴望血的盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,会袭击来到城里的观光客
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,到了晚上那盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着沾满被袭击客人血的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,高兴地数着「一件 两件」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,停停停
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这个不是这个梗的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我也听说过这样的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:19:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,战国时代战败阵亡的山梨县出身武士的盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢站起来说到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,桃子李子都是桃科
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\an7\fs30}※ 日本绕口令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,都是桃科…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,都是桃桃科
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,桃子猫尾…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,猫尾猫尾尾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,猫猫猫猫猫尾草
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8}别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这是猫尾草的歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,猫尾草
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8}等一下 不要丢下响
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,花子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这歌是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是猫尾草
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真的要进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么全都散架了却能听见猫尾草的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,恶灵退散恶灵退散
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,牡丹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,太狡猾了 响也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,脚脚脚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,奔跑的脚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,说到散架 我听说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,大约十年前  某国家的牧羊人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,脚 猫尾草的脚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,每天晚上一个人吃火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,火锅的话  是冬天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,咱现在说点有用的成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,某一天发现锅里肉都吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:20:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是贪吃鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,莲 响不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,别唱了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,明明散架了还唱Rap
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 放弃思考了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是个不错的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.51,0:21:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不错个鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.23,0:21:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,烟花开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.62,0:22:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,猫猫猫尾…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,暑假好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.13,0:22:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,于是面对着大朵的烟火
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.18,0:22:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,在心中刻下了夏日的回忆
